00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
the best sponge cake in the universe today here on SambaCooking

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.133
discover the true Italian recipe

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.533
was created in 1700 by a Genoese cook who accompanied

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
the marquis of Genoa on a journey with the Spanish royal family

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.600
he created a mix called Genoese pasta that was cooked in a water bath

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
and then in the oven for this recipe sponge cake that is all

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.600
put in cold and then cooked in the oven ... we proceed

00:00:05.859 --> 00:00:12.859
break 6 eggs in a planetary

00:00:14.959 --> 00:00:19.939
combine 180 grams of sugar

00:00:19.939 --> 00:00:23.569
a pinch of salt

00:00:23.569 --> 00:00:28.759
stir until mixture is smooth and even that will become clear

00:00:28.759 --> 00:00:35.789
Gradually

00:00:39.659 --> 00:00:42.059
when the eggs become very clear

00:00:42.059 --> 00:00:45.809
add the flour and potato starch

00:00:45.809 --> 00:00:48.449
sifting directly into the planetary

00:00:48.449 --> 00:00:52.759
also put a teaspoon of vanilla extract

00:00:52.759 --> 00:00:59.809
you can also use vanilla flavoring

00:01:03.959 --> 00:01:06.199
in a cake pan removable bottom

00:01:06.199 --> 00:01:07.649
pass the butter

00:01:07.649 --> 00:01:12.429
and the flour does not stick to the dough

00:01:12.429 --> 00:01:18.059
cook in preheated oven at 180 degrees for 40 minutes

00:01:18.059 --> 00:01:20.368
are the ingredients for a cake of

00:01:20.368 --> 00:01:27.368
26 cm

